{"tid":372090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"看到台妹失控 世大運選手強吻摸胸逼加Facebook","createTime":"2017-08-24T06:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T07:04:07.000Z","uid":55981,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"414b539db1edaa0ea23b905006588e37dc439aa1","tid":372090,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》昨接獲爆料，一名世大運女性工作人員21日在林口選手村戶外人行天橋，遭某外國男性選手強吻臉部、摸胸還逼加臉書，事後由世大運工作人員陪同報警，並轉報該國代表團處置運動員。<br />\n<br />\n世大運組委會昨晚證實有此性騷擾案，但基於尊重以及保護原則，組委會不便透露案情細節，相關單位已經處理此案中，已請此位女工作人員休息，或是改調其他地方、不要在選手村值勤，另已按照流程通報大會，及該代表團做後續處理。據了解，處置方式包括境管、停賽等。<br />\n<br />\n據透露，該名女性工作人員是位年輕正妹，對外籍男選手的舉動相當不舒服，經她反映被性騷擾後，組委會隨即按程序通報處理，並安撫其情緒。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170824/1189139/%E8%A6%8B%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E5%87%8D%E6%9C%AA%E6%A2%9D%E3%80%80%E4%B8%96%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8B%E6%B4%8B%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E8%AE%8A%E7%8B%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flocal%2F20170824%2F1189139%2F%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E5%2587%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25A2%259D%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%2596%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258B%25E6%25B4%258B%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25AE%258A%25E7%258B%25BC&d=5u6NhZoHHrEugB6bWmFGsS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b314140a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170824/1189139/%E8%A6%8B%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E5%87%8D%E6%9C%AA%E6%A2%9D%E3%80%80%E4%B8%96%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8B%E6%B4%8B%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E8%AE%8A%E7%8B%BC</a>"},{"pid":"844ac7cf5fdcb532b85966bf27c99839fcd72864","tid":372090,"uid":136455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"死鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d5ed370deed7bd0131b73149c09a79075c2d86","tid":372090,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy